Class TriviaQuestion

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.cnm.deepdive.triviagame.model.entity.TriviaQuestion

  • public class TriviaQuestion
extends Object
    This is the entity class that creates a TriviaQuestion object. Each TriviaQuestion object is associated with exactly one TriviaCategory.
